{"id":5460,"date":"2012-08-21T13:53:13","date_gmt":"2012-08-21T17:53:13","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=5460"},"modified":"2022-01-21T10:10:56","modified_gmt":"2022-01-21T06:10:56","slug":"honey-treatment-upset-stomach","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/21\/honey-treatment-upset-stomach\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Honey: The Prophet uses honey to treat upset stomach"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Abu Sa&#8217;id al-Khudri reported: A man came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, &#8220;My brother has diarrhea.&#8221; The Prophet said, &#8220;<strong>Give him honey to drink<\/strong>.&#8221; The man gave him honey to drink and he said, &#8220;I gave it to him but his diarrhea only got worse.&#8221; The Prophet said, &#8220;<strong>Allah has told the truth and your brother&#8217;s stomach is mistaken<\/strong>.&#8221; He gave him more honey and he was cured.<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5716, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2217<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Muttafaqun Alayhi<\/strong><\/em> (authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0631\u064e\u062c\u064f\u0644\u064c \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0623\u064e\u062e\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0633\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0637\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0642\u064e \u0628\u064e\u0637\u0652\u0646\u064f\u0647\u064f \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e <